	                            <td class="support-td-check support-td-check-50">
									Collaborate with co-teachers or special education colleagues in Capti via email messaging and by distributing content.<br><br>
									Use Capti as a way to accommodate your students’ specific needs
	                            </td>
	                        </tr>
	                        <tr>
	                            <td class="support-td-info support-td-info-50">Finding and juggling tools or strategies to help fill the existing gap</td>
	                            <td class="support-td-check support-td-check-50">An inclusion classroom challenge is that there too many tools that provide too little support. Capti is an all-in-one literacy solution that provides students and teachers with a platform for making their curriculum content more accessible.</td>
