					<p>Toni-Marie Ramos examines the disadvantages that many unsupported teachers face in inclusive classrooms. <br><a class="ed-link" target="_block" href="http://hubpages.com/education/Top-Challenges-Teacher-Face-in-Special-Needs-Inclusive-Classrooms">http://hubpages.com/education/Top-Challenges-Teacher-Face-in-Special-Needs-Inclusive-Classrooms</a></p>
